<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('fragments/head'); %>
  <body>
    <%- include('fragments/email-preview', { previewText: previewText }); %>

    <p>Hello <%= studentFirstName %>,</p>

    <p>
      Thank you for registering for the upcoming <%= courseName %>. You are receiving this email because your requested a billing invoice. Your invoice has been included as a PDF attachment to this email.
    </p>

    <p>
      Your course registration status is currently <b>pending</b> as we have not yet received your payment. You may complete your course registration using one of the following payment options:
    </p>

    <div>
      <h3>Online</h3>
      <p>
        Use our secure credit card payment page: 
        <a href="<%= creditPaymentLink %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          https://princeton-groundwater.com/payment/credit
        </a> 
      </p>
      <p>
        Your credit card payment will be processed by 
        <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Stripe</a>, 
        a trusted and PCI compliant online payment service. Your card information will be used for this single transaction and will not be stored on our servers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Check by Mail</h3>
      <p>
        Note that your check must be received and cleared 
        <strong>by <%= paymentDeadline %></strong>, 2 weeks before the start of the course.
      </p>

      <h4 class="subject-title">Payable To</h4>
      <div class="highlighted-subject">
        <div class="subject-details">
          Princeton Groundwater, Inc.
        </div>
      </div>

      <h4 class="subject-title">Mailing Address</h4>
      <div class="highlighted-subject">
        <div class="subject-details">
          <p>Princeton Groundwater, Inc.</p>
          <p>P.O. Box 273776</p>
          <p>Tampa, FL 33688-3776</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Bank Transfer (ACH)</h3>
      <p>
        You can transfer your payment using an ACH wire transfer. Note that your transfer must be received and cleared 
        <strong>by <%= paymentDeadline %></strong>, 2 weeks before the start of the course.
      </p>

      <h4 class="subject-title">Bank Address</h4>
      <div class="highlighted-subject">
        <div class="subject-details">
          <p>J.P. Morgan Chase Bank, N.A.</p>
          <p>12703 North Dale Mabry Highway</p>
          <p>Tampa, Florida</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h4 class="subject-title">Account Details</h4>
      <div class="highlighted-subject">
        <div class="subject-details">
          <p>Account number: 951634930</p>
          <p>ABA routing number: 267084131</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('fragments/footer', { contactEmail: contactEmail, contactPhone: contactPhone }); %>
  </body>
</html>
